data.title: Good fast food
data.text: We went there on Wednesday night 09/14. Was good fast food, but they got two out of our five orders messed up. They quickly replaced the items to correct their mistake. New corner location was clean.

data.title: Fast, Good and Reasonable
data.text: I get food from this Taco Bueno every other week. My grandson and I love the food. The food is fresh and good. Very little wait. The worker conduct is professional. Edifice inside and outside is clean. If you have never tryed Taco Bueno for sure you will like this one.

data.title: Fast Tex-Mex
data.text: This is an old establishment. It is clean, but needs an update. The service is fast, friendly, and efficient. Taste like every other Taco Bueno.

data.title: Worst Fast Food Experience Ever
data.text: This place was so bad, I had to write about it. We decided to get food here as we are from out of town and were very hungry. The order was completed accurately, although the window guy came off as rude and like he didn't want to be there. We just got home, and we can't even eat any of it. I don't know what they did to it, but it's ALL COMPLETELY inedible. I've never had fast food that was this bad before. Huge waste of 18 bucks and our time. Not worth the trouble to go back and get a refund. Stay away!!

data.title: Good fast food
data.text: Ok. I normally don't review fast food places but why is this location so good. They must put something in their food that keeps me coming. Taco Thursday's are the best. This location is awesomely wonderful. The tacos are really good

data.title: If Taco Bell and Pollo Loco Had a Baby...
data.text: It would be this place!  I really enjoyed it.  Super clean, very friendly service.  It was pretty busy, which is an indication of how good it was.  It is a quick service restaurant, but it is SO good.  I had a big freaking taco...no really that's what is called...a big freaking taco.  My husband loved the queso dip.  All good...no bad.
